.\n- [ ] Worker registered with master (master webui / worker logs).\n- [ ] SparkPi job `1/1` completed with correct output on target version.\n- [ ] No `ImagePullBackOff`, no OOMKilled, no `spark-nonexistent` references remain.\n- [ ] RBAC bindings unchanged or tightened as approved.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false}}
